<p>The more news pattern is for showing a list of news articles or blog posts that provide links to the full article. These are previous posts or articles that are not featured items.</p>

<h3>Rules for more news</h3>
<ul>
	<li>There must be a thumbnail image. Use a placeholder if an image is not available.</li>
	<li>The thumbnail image must always be positioned on the right.</li>
	<li>Thumbnail image must be 360px &times; 240px.</li>
	<li>There must not be more than 40 words in the excerpt and it must end with an ellipsis <code>&amp;hellip;</code> (&hellip;).</li>
	<li>If there are more than ten items on a page, then the page must use <a href="../pagination/index.html#pager">pager pagination</a>.</li>
</ul>

